<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Welcome to Our Paging System</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            color: #333;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #0066cc;
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 3em;
                margin: 0;
            }

            .header p {
                font-size: 1.2em;
                margin: 10px 0 0;
            }

        .welcome-section {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

            .welcome-section h2 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                color: #0066cc;
            }

            .welcome-section p {
                font-size: 1.2em;
                text-align: center;
                max-width: 800px;
            }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

            .feature-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }

            .feature-card h3 {
                color: #0066cc;
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }

            .feature-card p {
                font-size: 1em;
                color: #555;
            }

        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

            .cta-section a {
                background-color: #0066cc;
                color: white;
                padding: 15px 30px;
                border-radius: 30px;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-size: 1.2em;
                transition: background-color 0.3s;
            }

                .cta-section a:hover {
                    background-color: #004999;
                }

        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Paging System</h1>
        <p>Efficient, reliable, and easy to use.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="welcome-section">
        <h2>Manage Your Communication with Ease</h2>
        <p>
            Our paging system offers seamless and efficient communication across different platforms.
            Whether you're managing alerts, notifications, or scheduling tasks, our solution is built to deliver the best experience possible.
        </p>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>Real-time Alerts</h3>
                <p>Get instant notifications and keep track of important updates with our real-time alert system.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>Easy Scheduling</h3>
                <p>Manage all your tasks with a built-in scheduling tool that ensures you never miss a notification.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>Multi-Platform Support</h3>
                <p>Our system works across different devices, ensuring you stay connected wherever you are.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <a href="/signup">Get Started Today</a>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Paging System | Designed to keep you connected</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
